...keberanian.

00:13:15.181 --> 00:13:17.562
Kamu mengajariku kawan...

00:13:18.035 --> 00:13:19.964
...bahwa saya harus
mendukung apa yang benar.

00:13:20.712 --> 00:13:21.993
Karena itu...

00:13:22.271 --> 00:13:23.794
...Saya tidak...

00:13:24.973 --> 00:13:26.784
...denganmu.

00:13:27.863 --> 00:13:29.110
Saya...

00:13:29.343 --> 00:13:31.883
...mendukung Thakuma hari ini.

00:13:33.739 --> 00:13:34.960
Aku ingat...

00:13:35.257 --> 00:13:36.981
...semua yang kamu ajarkan padaku.

00:13:39.155 --> 00:13:41.325
